JSX :- 
       It is similar look like as HTML
       ex:- <h1>hello</h1>

Babel :-
       Babel is a Javascript compiler
       It is convert the JSX language to React.createElement
       If you use online then you bableCDN copy link then paste in HTML after closing body tage
       and link of JS his type name is "Text/babel" 

Create Element using JSX :-
                one element
        Ex :-    store variable = <h1>hello</h1>

